body_html:
Hey,

You can see the changed file and the .csv files here at the TensorFlow github page:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/examples/tutorials/monitors

Download the files to a folder and change:

# Data sets
IRIS_TRAINING = "iris_training.csv"
IRIS_TEST = "iris_test.csv"

to

# Data sets
IRIS_TRAINING = "<path_to_file>/iris_training.csv"
IRIS_TEST = "<path_to_file>/iris_test.csv"

body:
Hey,

You can see the changed file and the .csv files here at the [TensorFlow github page](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/examples/tutorials/monitors):
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/examples/tutorials/monitors

Download the files to a folder and change:

```
# Data sets
IRIS_TRAINING = "iris_training.csv"
IRIS_TEST = "iris_test.csv"

to

# Data sets
IRIS_TRAINING = "<path_to_file>/iris_training.csv"
IRIS_TEST = "<path_to_file>/iris_test.csv"
```
